description: 5 Dolla No Holla is taking NY Burroughs Fusion Street Food to the people of Louisville!With a delicious selection of sensational salads (like the fresh sym-bionic lettuce with Woodford Reserve gorgonzola thyme vinaigrette, blackberry cajun-roasted pistachios, roasted red pepper flakes, and leeks) and hand-crafted small batch ice cream (with delectable flavors like lemon goat cheese, peanut butter & jelly, salted caramel pretzel, etc...), this vintage trailer makes every occasion feel extra special. Invite this neat team to come cater your next event and no matter your preferences, they are happy to work with you to craft the perfect menu. With deliciousness in every dish, you and your guests will be all about 5 Dolla No Holla.
name: 5 Dolla No Holla
